---
title: Homemade Pita Bread & Chicken Shawarma Made From Scratch Bread Series - roll up your sleeves!
description: When you have a little extra time (a great weekend project!), bake these from-scratch pita breads for the best shawarma ever! You’ll mix, rest, and roll out dough while marinating chicken in yogurt, garlic, and spices. Sauté the chicken with onion, and serve it with a tangy, juicy feta, cucumber, and tomato salad plus warm homemade pitas.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66e876202d58b223b75b9a82-21c8bce6.jpeg
